OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Grab the children and     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fleave': BBC reporter flees 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FIsrael bomb warning        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It was just before 3pm in Gaza on      
OL,6, Tuesday. I was preparing to go live on 
OL,7, BBC TV News when I received a call from
OL,8, my wife - almost in tears, the kids    
OL,9, crying in the background.              
OL,11,FThey'd been told to leave the apartment
OL,12,Fwe'd been staying in because of a      
OL,13,Fwarning the Israeli air force was going
OL,14,Fto bomb next door.                     
OL,16,FI told her to grab the children and    
OL,17,Fleave immediately. My colleague Mahmoud
OL,18,Fwas nearby and I rang him to ask him to
OL,19,Fhelp.                                  
